    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of use here and there, but it still drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it, so it\u2019s all set for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it!",
      "price": 33900.0,
