    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a quintessential driver\u2019s specimen, featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant has been proactively serviced with an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit, mitigating the primary failure point of this architecture. Utilizing the Turbo-spec widebody chassis, this C4S offers superior lateral stiffness and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system for high-limit traction. The suspension geometry is stabilized by upgraded Bilstein dampers, while the braking system retains its factory four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled, ventilated rotors for exceptional thermal management. This vehicle presents in honest condition, with mechanical synchronization and throttle response that remain razor-sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
