    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is a meticulously maintained example of the ultimate performance SUV. Finished in Deep Black Metallic, the exterior retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014honest signs of careful road use. The interior features Luxor Beige leather that remains supple and smoke-free, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this Macan is superb; it comes with a full service history documenting consistent maintenance. The 3.0L V6 biturbo engine delivers smooth, robust power, and the PDK transmission shifts flawlessly. Recently fitted with a fresh set of tires and having passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this vehicle is turn-key and ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
